# Book Link

A full-stack web app where users build a virtual bookshelf and receive a personalized book recommendation.

**Live demo**: https://finalproject1-a9cc72696071.herokuapp.com/

#### Technologies: 
- Node.js
- Express
- MongoDB
- Google OAuth
- OpenLibrary API
- BigBook API

#### Features
- User authentication with Google OAuth
- Add, view, edit, and delete books
- Personalized book recommendation based on users shelf
- Responsive front-end design
